# 🔄 RAG Hybrid Search Pipeline — Visual Flowchart

> **File:** `5-rag-from-vectordb copy.py`
> A Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) chatbot that uses **hybrid search** (keyword + vector) over a PDF to answer questions via an LLM.

---

## End-to-End Pipeline

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    classDef initStyle fill:#1e1e2e,stroke:#89b4fa,stroke-width:2px,color:#cdd6f4
    classDef loadStyle fill:#1e1e2e,stroke:#a6e3a1,stroke-width:2px,color:#cdd6f4
    classDef indexStyle fill:#1e1e2e,stroke:#f9e2af,stroke-width:2px,color:#cdd6f4
    classDef searchStyle fill:#1e1e2e,stroke:#fab387,stroke-width:2px,color:#cdd6f4
    classDef llmStyle fill:#1e1e2e,stroke:#cba6f7,stroke-width:2px,color:#cdd6f4
    classDef decisionStyle fill:#1e1e2e,stroke:#f38ba8,stroke-width:2px,color:#cdd6f4
    classDef userStyle fill:#313244,stroke:#89dceb,stroke-width:2px,color:#cdd6f4

    subgraph INIT["⚙️ INITIALIZATION"]
        A["📦 Load Environment Variables<br/><i>.env → GROQ_API_KEY, MODEL_NAME</i>"]:::initStyle
        B["🤖 Initialize Groq LLM<br/><i>ChatGroq(model, api_key)</i>"]:::initStyle
        C["🧠 Load Embedding Model<br/><i>all-MiniLM-L6-v2</i>"]:::initStyle
    end

    subgraph LOAD["📄 STEP 1 — LOAD & SPLIT PDF"]
        D["📖 Load PDF<br/><i>PyPDFLoader('mcp.pdf')</i>"]:::loadStyle
        E["✂️ Split into Chunks<br/><i>chunk_size=1000, overlap=200</i>"]:::loadStyle
    end

    subgraph INDEX["📇 STEP 2 — BUILD SEARCH INDEXES"]
        F{"🗂️ FAISS index<br/>exists on disk?"}:::decisionStyle
        G["💾 Load existing FAISS index<br/><i>faiss_mcp_index/</i>"]:::indexStyle
        H["🏗️ Create new FAISS index<br/><i>from document chunks</i>"]:::indexStyle
        I["💾 Save FAISS index to disk"]:::indexStyle
        J["🔤 Build BM25 Keyword Retriever<br/><i>k=4 results</i>"]:::indexStyle
    end

    subgraph CHAT["💬 STEP 3 & 4 — INTERACTIVE CHAT LOOP"]
        K["👤 User enters a question"]:::userStyle
        L{"❓ Query == 'quit'?"}:::decisionStyle
        M["🔍 BM25 Keyword Search<br/><i>keyword_retriever.invoke(query)</i>"]:::searchStyle
        N["🔍 FAISS Vector Search<br/><i>similarity_search(query, k=4)</i>"]:::searchStyle
        O["🔀 Merge & Deduplicate<br/><i>Combine keyword + vector results</i>"]:::searchStyle
        P["📋 Build Context String<br/><i>Join all unique doc chunks</i>"]:::searchStyle
        Q["🧠 Send to Groq LLM<br/><i>'Answer based ONLY on context'</i>"]:::llmStyle
        R["💬 Display Bot Response"]:::llmStyle
    end

    S["🛑 Exit Program"]:::decisionStyle

    A --> B --> C
    C --> D --> E

    E --> F
    F -- "✅ Yes" --> G
    F -- "❌ No" --> H --> I
    G --> J
    I --> J

    J --> K
    K --> L
    L -- "Yes" --> S
    L -- "No" --> M
    L -- "No" --> N
    M --> O
    N --> O
    O --> P --> Q --> R
    R --> K
```

---

## Step-by-Step Breakdown

| Step | What Happens | Key Component | Purpose |
|:----:|:-------------|:-------------:|:--------|
| **⚙️** | Load `.env` secrets | `dotenv` | Securely load API keys |
| **⚙️** | Init LLM & Embeddings | `ChatGroq` + `HuggingFaceEmbeddings` | Set up the brain & encoder |
| **1** | Load & chunk the PDF | `PyPDFLoader` + `RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter` | Break document into searchable pieces |
| **2a** | Create/Load FAISS index | `FAISS` | Semantic (meaning-based) search |
| **2b** | Create BM25 retriever | `BM25Retriever` | Keyword (exact-match) search |
| **3** | Hybrid search on user query | Both retrievers + deduplication | Get the best of both search methods |
| **4** | LLM generates answer | `ChatGroq.invoke()` | Answer grounded in retrieved context |

---

## 🔑 Why Hybrid Search?

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    classDef vecStyle fill:#1e1e2e,stroke:#cba6f7,stroke-width:2px,color:#cdd6f4
    classDef kwStyle fill:#1e1e2e,stroke:#a6e3a1,stroke-width:2px,color:#cdd6f4
    classDef mergeStyle fill:#1e1e2e,stroke:#f9e2af,stroke-width:2px,color:#cdd6f4

    Q["🔎 User Query"]

    subgraph VEC["Vector Search (FAISS)"]
        V1["Understands meaning & synonyms"]:::vecStyle
        V2["'Who created MCP?' →<br/>finds 'Anthropic launched MCP'"]:::vecStyle
    end

    subgraph KW["Keyword Search (BM25)"]
        K1["Matches exact words & names"]:::kwStyle
        K2["'MCP November 2024' →<br/>finds exact date mentions"]:::kwStyle
    end

    M["🔀 Merge + Deduplicate"]:::mergeStyle
    R["📋 Richer, More Accurate Context"]:::mergeStyle

    Q --> VEC
    Q --> KW
    VEC --> M
    KW --> M
    M --> R
```

> [!TIP]
> **Vector search** catches semantically similar content (meaning-based), while **BM25 keyword search** catches exact term matches. Together, they provide more comprehensive retrieval than either method alone.
